#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/receiving_tickets.rst:13
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Helpdesk --> Configuration --> Teams` and choose an "
"existing team, or click :guilabel:`New` to :doc:`create a new team "
